import { Box, Center, FormControl, FormLabel, Heading, Input, Text } from "@chakra-ui/react";


const Login = () => {

    return(
        <>
            <Box height={"100vh"} bgColor={"#F5F7FA"} bgSize={"cover"}>
                <Center display={"flex"} justifyContent={"center"} alignItems={"center"}>
                    <Box bgColor={"#FFFFFF"} padding={"50px"} display={"flex"} justifyContent={"space-between"}>
                        <Heading>Welcome Admin.!</Heading>
                        <Text>Please Input Your Username and Password For Get Access</Text>

                        <FormControl>
                            <FormLabel>
                                Username
                            </FormLabel>
                            <Input value={"username"}></Input>

                            <FormLabel>
                                Password
                            </FormLabel>
                            <Input value={"password"}></Input>
                        </FormControl>
                    </Box>
                </Center>
            </Box>
        </>
    )
};

export default Login;
